Package: pagoda2
Title: Single Cell Analysis and Differential Expression
Version: 0.1.3
Authors@R: c(person("Peter", "Kharchenko", email = "peter_kharchenko@hms.harvard.edu", role = "aut"), person("Nikolas","Barkas", email="nikolas_barkas@hms.harvard.edu", role="aut"), person("Viktor", "Petukhov", email="viktor.s.petuhov@ya.ru", role="aut"), person("Evan", "Biederstedt", email="evan.biederstedt@gmail.com", role=c("cre", "aut")))
Description: Analyzing and interactively exploring large single-cell RNA-seq datasets. Pagoda2 primarily performs normalization and differential gene expression analysis, with an interactive application for exploring single-cell RNA-seq datasets. The package also serves as the primary method for pre-processing data for Conos, <https://github.com/kharchenkolab/conos>
Depends: R (>= 3.2.1), Matrix, igraph
